		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As far as I know, patents just show the early ideas, before they were implemented. They could have changed numerous things between the patent and the final product. So patents are a terrible &quot;source of information&quot; in this regard. They could be interesting to see how they came up with ideas though.

		

